    <div class="page-wrapper"><div id="main" class="main-wrapper"><div data-animation="default" class="navbar w-nav" data-wf--navbar--variant="base" data-easing2="ease" data-easing="ease" data-collapse="medium" data-w-id="fb272154-f29e-ab34-e878-15c4403e47b0" role="banner" data-duration="400"><div class="navbar-wrapper"><a href="/" aria-current="page" class="navbar-brand w-nav-brand w--current"><img loading="lazy" src="/dharmic-assets/dharmic-data-logo.svg" alt="Dharmic Data" class="nav-logo black"/></a><nav role="navigation" class="menu-wrapper w-nav-menu"><div class="menu-items"><a href="/" aria-current="page" class="nav-link w--current">Home</a><a href="/#mission" class="nav-link">Why us</a><a href="/#projects" class="nav-link">Projects</a><a href="/vlog" class="nav-link">Technical vlog</a></div></nav><div class="nav-buttons desk"><a data-wf--primary-button--variant="base" data-w-id="5e04e5d2-a7d2-705e-d362-7d1873101255" href="https://shakti.dharmicdata.org" class="primary-button w-inline-block"><div class="button-texts"><div class="button-text _01">Try Shakti</div><div class="button-text _02">Try Shakti</div></div></a></div><div class="menu-button w-nav-button"><div class="nav-lottie" data-w-id="fb272154-f29e-ab34-e878-15c4403e481e" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/assets/cdn/69158dc6-6915cadb447c3eeee558a1f7_Menu-Black-Hamburger.json" data-loop="0" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="0" data-duration="2.0020019204587935" data-loading="eager"></div><div class="menu-text _01">Menu</div><div class="menu-text _02">Cancel</div></div></div></div><section data-w-id="653b2948-49c4-c32e-b63a-70f84d615625" class="section home-hero"><div class="container"><div data-w-id="3c50132f-2a0b-16e8-9125-859e5e677ab5" class="wrapper home-hero"><div class="hero-contents home"><div data-w-id="6f30d9f5-f993-3688-8721-13a6b94a8ccb"><p data-wf--subtitle-text--variant="base" class="subtitle">Technology in service of people</p></div><div class="div-block"><div data-w-id="606f2837-0d5c-a39e-e1b3-943c0ca7dad4" class="hero-flex"><h1 class="dharmic-primary-heading"><span class="hero-title">Build</span> <span class="cta-title digital">Something Useful</span> <span class="hero-title">And Show</span> <span class="cta-title partner">How It Works</span></h1><img src="/assets/cdn/69577d21-695b7bc89eeea7bb104368a2_Frame-40.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Hero Star" class="hero-star"/><img src="/assets/cdn/69577d21-695b828603602d5c37661315_Vector.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Hero Icon" class="hero-icon left"/><img src="/assets/cdn/69577d21-695b8284add3e48c66f22636_Star-1.webp" loading="lazy" alt="Hero Icon" class="hero-icon right"/></div><p data-w-id="a2d24a18-361b-0a07-2ec0-785044013ee6" class="hero-para">Dharmic Data is building an open AI ecosystem for social good. We publish working demos, source code, and dated tests so you can make useful technology for your community.</p></div><div data-w-id="6da00be6-c186-04e6-295a-e480e5576993"><a data-wf--primary-button--variant="black" data-w-id="5e04e5d2-a7d2-705e-d362-7d1873101255" href="https://shakti.dharmicdata.org" class="primary-button w-variant-e28ee448-7aef-9746-10fe-f6086371a8a4 w-inline-block"><div class="button-texts"><div class="button-text _01">Try Shakti</div><div class="button-text _02">Try Shakti</div></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="home-rive"><canvas style="height:100%;width:100%"></canvas></div></section><section id="mission" class="section about"><div class="container"><div class="wrapper about"><div data-w-id="b2c65ac1-e431-797e-a086-2b7ccf743b9f" class="about-top"><div data-w-id="88fa43f4-c40e-0e4a-e8f6-12d4a59e2aec"><p data-wf--subtitle-text--variant="white-uppercase" class="subtitle w-variant-6d1b91dd-f7bb-09e9-d75d-cd5fa252e5c2">Why Dharmic Data</p></div><h2 class="about-title desk"><span class="dharmic-blank">Dharmic Data</span> We make and document software that serves people. We show the public need, the data, the code, the test, and the limit.</h2><h2 data-w-id="8a8fde9e-fd8b-a495-b2b1-079b3ed476b5" class="about-title mob">We make and document software that serves people. We show the public need, the data, the code, the test, and the limit.</h2><p data-w-id="7767d6f8-ae6e-039c-f38b-29597d708e3e" class="about-para">We use "dharmic" to describe work guided by service and responsibility. Dharmic Data is independent. It does not represent a public agency or a faith community.</p><div data-w-id="0cb2633f-244d-8c3a-59ca-4dd8e8937b75"><a data-wf--primary-button--variant="white" data-w-id="5e04e5d2-a7d2-705e-d362-7d1873101255" href="https://shakti.dharmicdata.org" class="primary-button w-variant-b40dcd44-b707-5b8f-a2a6-302004093bf4 w-inline-block"><div class="button-texts"><div class="button-text _01">Try Shakti</div><div class="button-text _02">Try Shakti</div></div></a></div><img src="/assets/cdn/69577d21-695bac5e662b2637d0a2b9bb_Union-1-.webp" loading="lazy" data-w-id="c103e9ea-d886-e7db-cbab-56c62df4a60d" alt="About Icon" class="about-icon _01"/><img src="/assets/cdn/69577d21-695bac73c7e2c5ecbd1b1673_Vector-1-.webp" loading="lazy" data-w-id="f8d9e758-1310-be7f-a7b3-5418bf8d5818" alt="About Icon" class="about-icon _02"/><img src="/assets/cdn/69577d21-695bac82662b2637d0a2c018_-.svg" loading="lazy" data-w-id="8e5fe1f9-63a9-c27f-d996-1c9f8d07f76c" alt="About Icon" class="about-icon _03"/><img src="/assets/cdn/69577d21-695bac98115543b08b895341_-.svg" loading="lazy" data-w-id="00e41227-4b09-e475-fb23-104e50297450" alt="About Icon" class="about-icon _04"/><div data-w-id="591d942a-23b2-8c63-04f2-6994a7fc6792" class="growth-text _01">Service-first</div><div data-w-id="56c7037c-a833-c38b-faca-6de91a87c619" class="growth-text _02">Evidence-led</div></div><div data-w-id="96e90ece-740e-dc68-471a-489ef84095b8" class="pill-drops"><div class="about-bottom"><div class="about-pills"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, -50rem, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(-90deg) sk